of Donyale.

00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:59.880
So I really felt like
God had chosen me

00:28:59.880 --> 00:29:06.140
as a child to provide
songs that could inspire

00:29:06.140 --> 00:29:07.290
and that could heal.

00:29:07.290 --> 00:29:09.990
And so after that,
I went to college,

00:29:09.990 --> 00:29:12.070
I went to Brown University,
kept on writing.

00:29:12.070 --> 00:29:14.010
Then I took a job at
"Essence" magazine

00:29:14.010 --> 00:29:16.584
and became the entertainment
editor of "Essence."

00:29:16.584 --> 00:29:18.500
And I served in that
position for seven years.

00:29:18.500 --> 00:29:19.740
And that was a great
networking place.

00:29:19.740 --> 00:29:21.430
And so while I was
there hanging out,

00:29:21.430 --> 00:29:26.670
I met a wonderful lady, Phyllis
Hyman, may she rest in peace.

00:29:26.670 --> 00:29:29.560
And she took me under her wing,
and I also met Queen Latifah.

00:29:29.560 --> 00:29:31.290
And so Queen Latifah
and Phyllis Hyman

00:29:31.290 --> 00:29:34.730
