Dave Hall, and then

00:29:40.520 --> 00:29:42.830
started writing some
of the songs that

00:29:42.830 --> 00:29:46.900
became number one hits and
sold millions of records.

00:29:46.900 --> 00:29:47.430
God is good.

00:29:47.430 --> 00:29:49.870
So some of those songs
include, Anita Baker's

00:29:49.870 --> 00:29:54.070
